It feels very weak when winding and leaves the impression that the first time it gets even a glancing blow that it will snap. I ended up wearing them more than expected and thus had to replace them a lot sooner than what is the norm for me. The reason I wore them so much is due to the styling. In other words, they go well with a pair of jeans and even in business casual attire.Although the shoes are a bit pricey in comparison to other casual shoes on the market, the Geox has a few features which justify the cost for me. First, is the styling which - as mentioned above - allows me to wear them most anytime. Second is that they are really comfortable. The first pair I obtained were a wide size and fit quite well. For my second pair, I was not able to locate a wide size and so I opted to buy a shoe that was a half size bigger. So far, so good in this regard.The other thing about these shoes is that do a good job of repelling foot odor. Evidently this is a patented feature of Geox shoes and, I must say, that my shoes never really failed me in this regard. And, I must admit that my feet can get a bit sweaty after a day of walking around in warm tempratures.Needless to say, the fact that I bought a second pair is indication in and of itself that I am happy with the shoes. If I had a complaint, it is in the fact that these shoes are hard to find. I actually searched for quite a while to find this shoe in the right color and in a size that I felt I could live with. I hope the search will be easier when it comes time to buy the next pair.","title":"Great shoe for different situations","username":"Christopher J."},{"dateAdded":"2015-09-20T20:42:28Z","dateSeen":["2015-09-19T00:00:00Z"],"sourceURLs":["http://www.amazon.com/Geox-Fast11-Driving-Moccasin-Coffee/dp/B005BSRACC"],"text":"Very comfortable, very predictable fit. I do not wear socks, to the fact that the shoe breaths better than normal shoes is a plus . . . for everyone around me. I've probably had 6 - 8 pair of these type of Geox shoes (various colors) and they are always my casual go to shoe.","title":"Very comfortable, very predictable fit","username":"Walter"}]

I finally sent them back because the foot leather is stiff and they are heavy. Also. the large heel, which should add stability on rough ground, has a square edge that makes walking cumbersome.
